modName: Aradias Leather Thief Armor Black - UNPB TBBP HDT w Bonus Textures
summary: Rare retextured armor that was sort of messed up so I fixed it and added it to the site, requires HDT High Heels system. Along with bonus all white, white/blue/orange, and white/blue/black/orange textures. More coming soon.
descriptionHtml:
Rare retextured armor that was sort of messed up so I fixed it and added it to the site, requires HDT High Heels system. Along with bonus all white, white/blue/orange, and white/blue/black/orange textures. More coming soon.
This edit was by someone else, however the bonus textures were by me. I don't know for sure if I'm allowed to do this. But I intend to take no one's idea. Only add to the available mods here.
This mod is originally by Aradia.

Install
It is a standalone, so just use NMM or drag and drop the contents in the TES directory

Location
The armor is Japanese so the only way to find it would be going to the forge, go to Glass and
look for the default characters (Rectangles).


Requires
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36213
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900
author: Aradia
